net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.event

Class ApplicationEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.event.Event
        • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.event.NotificationEvent
          • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.event.ApplicationEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ApplicationEvent
extends NotificationEvent
    This event is fired when application level events occurred, such as an application being started or stopped. Custom application events may use the constructor that takes a custom object as a parameter or may extend this event and may add whatever fields and methods necessary.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
